  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In CHF central sympathetic activity is increased. ROS formation seems to play a role in this
      process. This study analyzes the effect of vitamin C as an antioxidant on central sympathetic
      activity in CHF
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
